ZH: 万恶之源是贪婪。
EN: Greed is the root of all evil.

ZH: 万恶之首是无知。
EN: Ignorance is the chief evil.

ZH: 万恶莫过于欺骗。
EN: Deception is the worst of all evils.

ZH: 万恶之门已经打开。
EN: The gate of evil has been opened.

ZH: 万恶的种子已经播下。
EN: The seeds of evil have been sown.

ZH: 万恶奴隶制度已经废除。
EN: The evil of slavery has been abolished.

ZH: 万恶之地成为了废墟。
EN: The land of evil has become a ruin.

ZH: 万恶的事情总会有报应。
EN: Evil deeds will always have consequences.

ZH: 万恶皆在这个城市。
EN: All evil lies in this city.

ZH: 万恶的势力正在蔓延。
EN: The power of evil is spreading.

ZH: 万恶之地已经被诅咒。
EN: The land of evil has been cursed.

ZH: 万恶的影响一直存在。
EN: The influence of evil has always been present.

ZH: 万恶的阴谋正在被揭露。
EN: The conspiracy of evil is being exposed.

ZH: 万恶之人必将受到惩罚。
EN: The evildoer will be punished.

ZH: 万恶无不从于贪欲。
EN: All evils derive from greed.

ZH: 万恶如何可以被消除？
EN: How can evil be eradicated?

ZH: 万恶之源已经被发现。
EN: The source of all evil has been identified.

ZH: 万恶的城市被彻底毁灭。
EN: The city of evil was completely destroyed.

ZH: 万恶之道并非正确之道。
EN: The path of evil is not the right path.

ZH: 万恶不在於行为，而在於心灵。
EN: Evil lies not in actions, but in the heart.
